        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Jane hesitated, paused, looked at her aunt's guests as if almost surprised to find them there.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "But there, behind the scenes, in the semi darkness of screens and curtains, a fresh surprise awaited Jane, more startling than the enthusiastic tumult of her audience.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "At the foot of the staircase stood Garth Dalmain.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000023_000001",
