        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "\"Go back!\" he said, and the overmastering need quivering in his voice drew Jane's eyes to his in mute astonishment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "\"Go back at once and sing it all over again, note for note, word for word, just as before.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000024_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000024_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Go back now!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000024_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000024_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Go back at once!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000024_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000024_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Don't you know that you MUST?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Jane looked into those shining eyes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Something she saw in them excused the brusque command of his tone.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000025_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000025_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Without a word, she quietly mounted the steps and walked across the platform to the piano.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000025_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000025_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "People were still applauding, and redoubled their demonstrations of delight as she appeared; but Jane took her seat at the instrument without giving them a thought.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "She was experiencing a very curious and unusual sensation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000026_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000026_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "An unreasonable order, or a reasonable one unexplained, promptly met with a point blank refusal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "She had many finer songs in her repertoire.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000028_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000028_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "The audience expected another.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Why should she disappoint those expectations because of the imperious demands of a very highly excited boy?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "She commenced the magnificent prelude to Handel's \"Where'er you walk,\" but, as she played it, her sense of truth and justice intervened.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000029_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000029_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "While she played the Handel theme-and played it so that a whole orchestra seemed marshalled upon the key board under those strong, firm finger-she suddenly realised, though scarcely understanding it, the MUST of which Garth had spoken, and made up her mind to yield to its necessity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "His face was just as white as before, but his eyes had lost that terrible look of unshed tears, which had sent her back, at his bidding, without a word of question or remonstrance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000031_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000031_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "She smiled as she came slowly down the steps, and held out both hands to him with an unconscious movement of gracious friendliness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "For a moment he did not speak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "Then in a low voice, vibrant with emotion: \"My God!\" he said, \"Oh, my God!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "\"Hush,\" said Jane; \"I never like to hear that name spoken lightly, Dal.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "\"Spoken lightly!\" he exclaimed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-238_122530_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/238/122530/238_122530_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-238",
        "content": "\"So you liked my song?\" she said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
